law.catch_line: Agreements with public or private agencies.
law.text: The department may enter into agreements with public or private agencies in order to implement and operate the program created by KRS Chapter 197.
law.history: Amended 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 211, sec. 66, effective July 14, 1992. -- Created 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 478, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1986.
